<div class="content" name="Browser" uuid="ca16f0c1-5b3d-4f93-80cb-533657413e3f"><p>The browser interface lists the methods associated with the <a href="48f4ceaf-3cd0-4964-a964-2f4682b8d2f0#gt_f06aa0c1-29ec-4d3e-a4e2-e38e8f918933" data-linktype="relative-path">browser</a> service, which
creates and maintains a view of resources available on a network. The server
does not maintain <a href="48f4ceaf-3cd0-4964-a964-2f4682b8d2f0#gt_60e0e1fa-66fe-41e1-b5e3-ceab97e53506" data-linktype="relative-path">client</a>
state information. The protocol operation is stateless. The version for this
interface is 0.0. </p><p>The <a href="48f4ceaf-3cd0-4964-a964-2f4682b8d2f0#gt_c4813fc3-b2e5-4aa3-bde7-421d950d68d3" data-linktype="relative-path">UUID</a>
